@database
@wordwrap
## I wove wordwrap

@node main
This directory contains a Locate data file 'CDs.loc.' It is an example of how the data field labels can be modified for use in storing lists other than Addresses. This function hardly makes for a configurable database but it allows some extremely minor cosmetic flexibility.

In the Rexx drawer located in the EverydayOrganiser drawer, you will find a script called 'Locate_CD_Stats.rexx.' After loading the above mentioned data file into Locate, run this ARexx script via the ARexx menu 'Run New Script' or 'Install...'
@endnode
